# Frontend Conventions

## Stack

- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- Vitest + React Testing Library for tests
- `VITE_API_BASE_URL` from environment

## Acting-User Selector

- Load users from `GET /users`
- Store selected user ID in React context
- API client attaches `X-User-Id` on every request
- Show disclaimer: demo mode, not authenticated

## Error Handling

- Parse API error responses; display `detail` and field errors
- Shared error display component for forms and pages

## API Client

- Centralize fetch logic with base URL and headers
- Do not scatter `X-User-Id` across components

## Tests

- Colocate `*.test.tsx` with components or under `src/`
- Mock API for component tests
